578
01:09:27,080 --> 01:09:28,490
Không phải thật.

579
01:09:31,680 --> 01:09:32,880
Harry?

580
01:09:37,720 --> 01:09:38,920
Harry!

581
01:09:40,440 --> 01:09:43,360
- Harry!
